

To select the CIV CLQs:
========================================================================================================

((PLATE == 2089) && (FIBER == 427) && (MJD == 53498))  ||  ((PLATE == 2948) && (FIBER == 614) && (MJD == 54553))



Combination of Hamann et al. (2017) and Kozłowski (2017).

    Hamann et al. (2017) has     216188   objects
    Kozłowski (2017))    has     297301	  objects. 


"The_DF" in matchingHam17toKoz17.py then produces a joint catalog of 216188 objects.



