TOPCAP subsamples
========================================================================================================
From the full 297301 objects you then have these subsamples::

     L1350>0	     	     	      	   229248	77% 	
     (L1350>0) && (Mi >-40)		   229180	77%
     z >1.49999	      			   229193	77%


Concentrating on the 216188 Ham17 objects::
     L1350 > 40				   215842	100% 	




So, ~94% of the Ham17 sample is in the Full sample with a z_min >1.50 cut.
